--- !u!114 &658875211
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 658875206}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3de2f0312f140614a8517275a9592f8d, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueOn: 0
  player: {fileID: 21389782}
  dialogueTextGO: {fileID: 1416828780}
  animator: {fileID: 658875210}
  dialogueTextIntro:
  - 'Hey kid! Welcome to my gym. '
  - "So, you wanna take part in the Midnight Combat fightin\u2019 ring, eh? "
  - "Well if you wanna learn how to fight, you\u2019ve come to the right place! "
  - "Let\u2019s start with the basics, use <sprite name=\"M1\"> and <sprite name=\"M2\">
    on mouse and keyboard or <sprite name=\"LT\"> and <sprite name=\"RT\"> on controller
    to throw some punches. "
  dialogueTextPunchUp:
  - 'If you hold <sprite name="W"> or <sprite name="StickUp"> while punching, you
    can aim for your opponent''s head. '
  dialogueTextDodge:
  - "Nice work! Of course, in a real fight your opponent isn\u2019t just gonna let
    you hit them. Your best shot at landing a hit is right after avoiding an attack
    from your opponent. "
  - 'Try dodging these attacks using <sprite name="A"> and <sprite name="D"> or <sprite
    name="StickLeft"> and <sprite name="StickRight"> . '
  dialogueTextDuck:
  - "You got it! Some attacks can only be avoided by ducking underneath with <sprite
    name=\"S\"> or <sprite name=\"StickDown\"> . Why don\u2019t you give it a shot?  "
  dialogueTextParry:
  - "You\u2019re a natural! Now listen up \u2018cause this next part\u2019s important... "
  - 'Certain attacks can be parried if you press <sprite name="Space"> or <sprite
    name="EButton"> right before you get hit. '
  - 'You can tell these attacks apart from normal ones by the green glow around your
    opponent''s fist. '
  - "Let\u2019s see if you can parry these attacks with <sprite name=\"Space\"> or
    <sprite name=\"EButton\"> . "
  dialogueTextSpar:
  - "Not bad at all kid! That\u2019s about all the basics of fighting. How about
    you keep sparring with the bot to get some more practice in? "
  - Keep in mind, the best time to throw some punches is right after dodging or parrying
    and attack.
  dialogueTextSparWin1:
  - "Good work, are you sure you\u2019re new at thi-"
  dialogueTextSparWin2:
  - Sorry about that kid, seems the bot went a bit out of control after all that
    damage it took.
  - 'Good news though! While you were out of it, I got you booked in for a fight. '
  - 'I gotta good feeling about you kid. I think you might just make it to the top! '
  dialogueTextSparLose:
  - "You alright kid? Don\u2019t worry I\u2019ll get you patched up real quick."
  - 'Good news though! While you were out of it, I got you booked in for a fight. '
  - 'I gotta good feeling about you kid. I think you might just make it to the top! '
  dialogueTextCurrent: []
  dialogueEnded: 0
